{"tid":2517474,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"（多圖 ）死狗公香港電台DJ 李志剛 多次咸豬手女藝人 事後搏懵稱得許可","createTime":"2021-05-05T10:37:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T10:54:35.000Z","uid":198900,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ba58215dad6e696d9c65e2a6b91dd081c0e988b6","tid":2517474,"uid":198900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T10:37:19.000Z","msg":"AOA 雪炫慘遭港台DJ李志剛非禮<br />\n上星期五「第六屆香港亞洲流行音樂節」，主持之一的香港電台DJ 李志剛，台上無厘頭向表演嘉賓韓國女團AOA成員雪炫擁抱，結果消息燒到韓國大堆Fans 網民眼火爆。<br />\n主要的指控是李志剛<span class=\"red\">「一副嘟嘴狼胎猴擒樣」，又無端端伸腳疑似觸碰雪炫下體。</span>不過本人認為事後李志剛的解釋先最出事，因為他聲稱要求擁抱的原因是配合大會主題「擁抱音樂」。另外他又辯稱當時經台上繙譯詢問，得雪炫許可，並非強行抽水。一方面話「希望fans 唔好唔開心」，同時又話<span class=\"red\">「我自己就好開心」</span>。<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.weserv.nl/?url=40.media.tumblr.com/8c46d9d19f688958382ab3fdffbe8569/tumblr_o4dtgisPLc1v1wng1o1_540.jpg&amp;h=460&amp;output=webp&amp;q=80&amp;we&amp;errorredirect=40.media.tumblr.com/8c46d9d19f688958382ab3fdffbe8569/tumblr_o4dtgisPLc1v1wng1o1_540.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.weserv.nl%2F%3Furl%3D40.media.tumblr.com%2F8c46d9d19f688958382ab3fdffbe8569%2Ftumblr_o4dtgisPLc1v1wng1o1_540.jpg%26h%3D460%26output%3Dwebp%26q%3D80%26we%26errorredirect%3D40.media.tumblr.com%2F8c46d9d19f688958382ab3fdffbe8569%2Ftumblr_o4dtgisPLc1v1wng1o1_540.jpg&h=d6075b66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images.weserv.nl/?url=41.media.tumblr.com/59e9537f1d5b05244668e0b080447aeb/tumblr_o4dtgisPLc1v1wng1o2_1280.jpg&amp;h=460&amp;output=webp&amp;q=80&amp;we&amp;errorredirect=41.media.tumblr.com/59e9537f1d5b05244668e0b080447aeb/tumblr_o4dtgisPLc1v1wng1o2_1280.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.weserv.nl%2F%3Furl%3D41.media.tumblr.com%2F59e9537f1d5b05244668e0b080447aeb%2Ftumblr_o4dtgisPLc1v1wng1o2_1280.jpg%26h%3D460%26output%3Dwebp%26q%3D80%26we%26errorredirect%3D41.media.tumblr.com%2F59e9537f1d5b05244668e0b080447aeb%2Ftumblr_o4dtgisPLc1v1wng1o2_1280.jpg&h=7f312361&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wDj7gNl5nQs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwDj7gNl5nQs&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn1EyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=11054a41\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wDj7gNl5nQs</a><br />\n4:40開始<br />\n咸豬手李志剛有前科<br />\n李志剛今次發到咁大，主要因為他疑似有前科。2006年香港電台「太陽計劃」記者會玩寵物美容（又係無厘頭），當時主持李志剛以狗毛公仔質向衛詩心口。事後<span class=\"red\">李志剛就話大家熟，玩下無事。但衛詩受傳媒訪問直認尷尬，「有叫唔好」，而且2人唔熟。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://images.weserv.nl/?url=40.media.tumblr.com/d5c36a58dac3025301e078e6d9fd2ce3/tumblr_o4dwp0vgWB1v1wng1o4_400.jpg&amp;h=460&amp;output=webp&amp;q=80&amp;we&amp;errorredirect=40.media.tumblr.com/d5c36a58dac3025301e078e6d9fd2ce3/tumblr_o4dwp0vgWB1v1wng1o4_400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.weserv.nl%2F%3Furl%3D40.media.tumblr.com%2Fd5c36a58dac3025301e078e6d9fd2ce3%2Ftumblr_o4dwp0vgWB1v1wng1o4_400.jpg%26h%3D460%26output%3Dwebp%26q%3D80%26we%26errorredirect%3D40.media.tumblr.com%2Fd5c36a58dac3025301e078e6d9fd2ce3%2Ftumblr_o4dwp0vgWB1v1wng1o4_400.jpg&h=3f14caf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images.weserv.nl/?url=40.media.tumblr.com/e02df92dece2ada6ce898aa3b5d9ba2f/tumblr_o4dwp0vgWB1v1wng1o5_1280.jpg&amp;h=460&amp;output=webp&amp;q=80&amp;we&amp;errorredirect=40.media.tumblr.com/e02df92dece2ada6ce898aa3b5d9ba2f/tumblr_o4dwp0vgWB1v1wng1o5_1280.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.weserv.nl%2F%3Furl%3D40.media.tumblr.com%2Fe02df92dece2ada6ce898aa3b5d9ba2f%2Ftumblr_o4dwp0vgWB1v1wng1o5_1280.jpg%26h%3D460%26output%3Dwebp%26q%3D80%26we%26errorredirect%3D40.media.tumblr.com%2Fe02df92dece2ada6ce898aa3b5d9ba2f%2Ftumblr_o4dwp0vgWB1v1wng1o5_1280.jpg&h=74d2e4f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢條撚樣幾時死？人又樣衰，仲影衰香港人"},{"pid":"003745b560d03808d085165c5e85b0ed6a69f5af","tid":2517474,"uid":131696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T10:40:23.000Z","msg":"佢好似gay的<br />\n定扮gay食女？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":